languages.text: "Я удовлетворила твое любопытство? Тогда — услуга за услугу. В нагрудном кармане пачка лхо. Угости меня одной, остальные забирай себе. Я сегодня в очень щедром настроении".
"Have I sated your curiosity? Then I'd like my favour returned. There's a pack of lho in my breast pocket. Give me one, and you can keep the rest. I'm feeling very generous today."

languages.text: « Ai-je satisfait votre curiosité ? Si oui, j'aimerais que vous me rendiez service à votre tour. Il y a un paquet de lho dans ma poche de poitrine. Donnez-moi une tige, vous pourrez garder le reste. Je suis d'humeur très généreuse, aujourd'hui. »
languages.original_text: "Have I sated your curiosity? Then I'd like my favour returned. There's a pack of lho in my breast pocket. Give me one, and you can keep the rest. I'm feeling very generous today."

languages.text: «¿He saciado su curiosidad? En ese caso, me gustaría que me devolviera el favor. Tengo una cajetilla de lho en el bolsillo del pecho. Déme uno y quédese con el resto. Hoy me siento muy generosa».
languages.original_text: "Have I sated your curiosity? Then I'd like my favour returned. There's a pack of lho in my breast pocket. Give me one, and you can keep the rest. I'm feeling very generous today."

languages.text: “我有没有满足你的好奇心？那我希望你能还我个人情。我胸前的口袋里有包麻烟。给我一根，剩下的你都可以留着，我今天挺大方的。”
languages.original_text: "Have I sated your curiosity? Then I'd like my favour returned. There's a pack of lho in my breast pocket. Give me one, and you can keep the rest. I'm feeling very generous today."

languages.text: 「あんたの好奇心は満たされたかな？ならば、礼をしてもらいたいね。胸のポケットにエルホのパックがある。一つ私にくれたら、残りはあんたにやろう。今日はとても気前がいいんだ」
languages.original_text: "Have I sated your curiosity? Then I'd like my favour returned. There's a pack of lho in my breast pocket. Give me one, and you can keep the rest. I'm feeling very generous today."

languages.text: "Habe ich Eure Neugier gestillt? Dann revanchiert Euch bitte. In meiner Brusttasche ist eine Packung Lho. Gebt mir eine, den Rest könnt Ihr behalten. Ich bin heute großzügig gestimmt."

languages.text: "Merakını giderebildim mi? O zaman karşılığında bir isteğim olacak. Göğüs cebimde bir paket liho olacaktı. Bana bir tane ver, gerisi senin olsun. Bugün çok cömertim."
